headline: ICE Transitions AMERIBOR速 to ICE Data Indices
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, October 01, 2025--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE:ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today announced the transition of the American Interbank Offered Rate, now ICE AMERIBOR速, to ICE Data Indices, LLC.
